---
title: Sweet-Soy Beef & Sesame Fries with Ponzu Cucumber Salad & Mayo
description: Sweet, savoury, and seriously crave-worthy! Sweet and savoury beef pairs perfectly with crispy sesame fries, a tangy ponzu cucumber salad, and a dollop of creamy mayo. It’s a flavor-packed feast that’ll have you coming back for one more bite!

